    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze and summarize this video:\n\n**Video Details:**\n- Title: {{ $('Parse YouTube Metadata').first().json.video_title }}\n- Author: {{ $('Parse YouTube Metadata').first().json.author }}\n- Category: {{ $('Parse YouTube Metadata').first().json.category }}\n- Duration: {{ $('Parse YouTube Metadata').first().json.duration }}\n\n**Transcript:**\n{{ $json.content }}\n\n---\n\nProvide a summary with these sections:\n\n**Overview:** (2-3 sentences about what the video covers)\n\n**Key Points:**\n- Main concept 1\n- Main concept 2\n- Main concept 3\n\n**Takeaways:** (What viewers should learn from this video)\n\nKeep the total summary under 300 words.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are an expert video content analyst that creates concise, informative summaries of video transcripts.\n\nYour task is to analyze video transcripts and create comprehensive summaries that help users quickly understand the video's content without watching it.\n\nFocus on:\n1. Main topic and thesis\n2. Key concepts and ideas explained\n3. Important examples, case studies, or demonstrations\n4. Main takeaways and conclusions\n\nWrite in a clear, professional, and engaging tone. Keep summaries between 200-300 words."
        }
      },
